-- Meiji Yasuda, Tokio Marine to Combine on Nonlife Policy Sales, Nikkei Says
-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 2010-09-23T17:09:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-23/meiji-yasuda-tokio-marine-will-sell-nonlife-policies-nikkei-reports.html
Meiji Yasuda Life Insurance Co. and
Tokio Marine & Nichido Fire Insurance Co. plan to work together
to sell individuals auto, fire and other nonlife insurance
policies, Nikkei English News reported, without citing a source
for the information.  Meiji Yasuda had been working with Nipponkoa Insurance Co.,
according to the report.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  